fields.name: Guinness 0.0
fields.description: Aroma: Sweet smelling with a coffee and malty nose. Flavour: Perfect balance of bitter and sweet with malt and roast characters. Palate: Smooth, creamy and balanced. Appearance: A characteristically dark, ruby coloured liquid.

fields.name: Apostel Weissbier
fields.description: Non-Alcoholic“ is brewed with the best wheat and barley malts. Thanks to the special brewing process, it retains its typical malty-fruity Weissbier taste, its full-bodied aroma and its lively character.

fields.name: Baltika
fields.description: This alcohol-free beer began production in 2001. It has a mild taste with a gorgeous malt aroma and ideally corresponds to the classic beer style. The ingredients are water, pale barley malt, maltose syrup and hops.

fields.name: Bavaria 0.0%
fields.description: Bavaria 0.0% Original has a distinct beer character: with a slightly hop-like and malt aroma, a full body, and a grainy and sweet flavour from the sugars in the barley Malt that beautifully balance the bitter tones of the beer.

fields.name: Carlsberg 0.0%
fields.description: Refreshing tasting with a crisp hoppy bite, Carlsberg 0.0 alcohol-free beer is everything you'd expect from a well-balanced Pilsner…just crafted to contain zero alcohol, and half the calories of our regular Pilsner. So now we can enjoy great-tasting beer any time. Skål!Probably no the best beer in the world

fields.name: Clausthaler Grapefruit
fields.description: A perfect blend of Clausthaler Original Non-Alcoholic Beer and Grapefruit Drink made with all-natural grapefruit juice. Clausthaler Non-Alcoholic Grapefruit is the first Grapefruit non-alcoholic blended beer in the U.S. and is the ultimate refreshment for any occasion!

fields.name: Cobra
fields.description: The advertised alcohol content of Cobra Zero is 0% ABV, which means it's under the detectable limit of 0.03%. The low to no alcohol content and the ingredients suggests the alcohol is removed after fermentation. Cobra Beer is a smoother, less gassy lager, designed as the perfect accompaniment to curries and other Indian dishes.

fields.name: Corona Cero
fields.description: 100% Refreshing Taste. 0% Alcohol. Moderate malty and grainy aromas, with slight fruity and citrussy notes makes it a great partner for several cuisines: in particular Thai, Chinese and Mexican

fields.name: Corona Sunbrew
fields.description: Corona Sunbrew 0.0% maintains Corona's essence; it was developed from Corona Extra by extracting the alcohol and then blending the non-alcoholic beer with vitamin D and natural flavours to reach the final recipe. Each 330 mL bottle contains 60 calories and 30 per cent of the daily value of vitamin D.

fields.name: Becks Blue
fields.description: Beck's Blue is a light, crisp and refreshing non-alcoholic alternative to beer, with no compromise on taste. And, at only 53 calories per bottle and fat-free, it makes the perfect light refreshment. Golden in colour, Beck's Blue is a classic German-style pilsner lager with over 140 years of heritage

fields.name: Erdinger Alkoholfrei
fields.description: Our non-alcoholic beer is a true multi-talent. Spicy malt notes harmonize excellently with caramel-sweet nuances. Enjoyment is enhanced by the stimulating bitterness of our aroma hops and a hint of light, fruity acidity. This is rounded out by finely sparkling carbonic acid

fields.name: Free-Damm
fields.description: Free Damm is a clean, sparkling, transparent amber colour with shades of gold. It has a light head and lively, fine bubbles. It has a clean, intense aroma, with hops taking centre stage and with hints of fresh white flowers. The taste is delicate, with suggestions of grains and toast.

fields.name: Gertel
fields.description: Non-Alcoholic Beer Pack Size 50cl Allergy Advice Barley - Contains Ingredients Water Barley Malt Carbon Dioxide Hop Extract Lower Age Limit

fields.name: Bigdrop Pale
fields.description: Alcohol-free Pale Ale. A delight for the senses, this beer delivers on all levels. Rosy floral aromas are immediate as you pour, with a light and limey citrus bite on the palate and a balanced but obvious bitterness to finish. Store and enjoy chilled.

fields.name: Lidl IPA
fields.description: Clear golden color with small off-white head. Aroma has caramel, grass. Taste is malty sweet with long somewhat bitter and quite sweet aftertaste. Flavors of grapefruit, grass, caramel.

fields.name: Birra Moretti Zero
fields.description: Birra Moretti, the ultimate Italian lager since 1859, proudly launches into the Low & No alcohol category with Moretti Zero. 0% alcohol, 100% Moretti. 66 Calories. Birra Moretti Zero's balanced flavour makes it the perfect accompaniment to meals - enjoy at lunch or dinner.

fields.name: Leffe Blonde 0.0%
fields.description: The first Leffe alcohol-free beer, Leffe Blonde 0,0% has a well-balanced body. Its slightly fruity notes associated with a bitter touch go perfectly with the characteristic flavour of cloves and hints of vanilla and smoky notes.

fields.name: Lomza 0.0%
fields.description: Perfect for when you're designated driver or you just fancy a cool refreshing beer without alcohol, Browar Lomza 0.0% is a light, zesty Pilsner with crisp clean malt and a clean aftertaste.

fields.name: Lucky Saint
fields.description: Progressively crafted with over 400 years of proud brewing heritage, Lucky Saint brings you an unfiltered beer that's alcohol-free yet full of flavour. Lucky Saint is born of Bavarian spring water, pilsner malt, hallertau hops and their single-use yeast for a unique lager that is unfiltered and uncompromising.

fields.name: Maisels-Weisse Alkoholfrei
fields.description: Maisel’s Weisse Alkoholfrei was crowned the World’s Best Alcohol Free Wheat Beer twice in a row in 2018 and 2019 at one of the best-known international beer competitions, the World Beer Award (London). Maisel’s Weisse Alkoholfrei is the ideal fitness and wellness drink for active and nutrition-conscious beer fans. Made only from natural raw materials but also contains vitamins, is isotonic, and has 33% fewer calories*. Maisel’s Weisse Alkoholfrei is a full-bodied and fruity taste typical of wheat beer – so wheat beer fans can enjoy their wheat beer.

fields.name: Moonlight
fields.description: Moonlight is a non-alcoholic hoppy ale brewed without compromise. Brewed with specialty malts, an abundance of juicy hops to make this non-alcoholic hoppy ale light in alcohol, but high in flavour. Expect juicy, citrus aromas with a clean fruity finish. Moonlight has only 46 calories per can and is vegan friendly.

fields.name: No Worries
fields.description: A lightly hopped and pleasantly refreshing pale ale, fermented with a brewers yeast which cant ferment Maltose. Tasting like a low abv beer due to this process you can enjoy the beer without the effect.

fields.name: Patronus
fields.description: Patronus is a Weissbier (or wheat beer) that cost something ridiculously cheap like 60 or 70 pence. Visually pours a cloudy sort of amber and a white head that holds fairly well. Despite not advertised as bottle conditioned, it must be to some degree as sediment is evident.

fields.name: Paulaner 0.0%
fields.description: Paulaner Weissbier 0,0% Strictly non-alcoholic available from Barry & Fitzwilliam. This non -alcohol beer has great flavour! Thanks to its balanced combination of fine malt aromas, refreshingly fruity Weissbier flavours and a pleasing hint of sweetness, our non-alcoholic Weissbier 0,0% can be enjoyed on any occasion.

fields.name: Perlenbacher 0.0%
fields.description: A clear golden beer with a rich creamy white head and adequate carbonation. Soft aroma with notes of hops, cereal, corn and bread. Slightly bitter flavour with notes of hops, grass and malts. Also hoppy aftertaste.

fields.name: Peroni Libera
fields.description: Zero Alcohol, Pure Style. Peroni Libera 0.0% is a light-bodied non-alcohol alternative for those who want to live their week fully without compromise. Peroni Libera 0.0% offers a refreshing and crisp taste with a fine bitterness and a fast and clean finish.

fields.name: Pure Brew
fields.description: The end product is a naturally brewed ulra-low alcohol lager full of flavour as you'd expect from us. A crisp, refreshing triple hopped lager at 0.5% ABV. Tripple Hopped lager with clean matly citrus notes.

fields.name: Radler
fields.description: Foster's Radler gives you the great refreshing taste of lager cut with thirst-quenching citrus flavour. Foster's Radler 0.0% gives you the same great Radler taste with no alcohol and is perfect for when you want to take it that little bit easier.

fields.name: Brewdog Punk AF
fields.description: All the attitude, all the flavour but none of the alcohol. Say hello to the Punkest non alcoholic beer in town. Juicy tropical fruit mixes it up with grassy and pine notes. All sitting on a solid malt bassline. Full flavour, no alcohol, all Punk.

fields.name: Brewdog Nanny State
fields.description: All creating a fully fruited hoppy ale that barely registers by alcohol. Resinous pine notes break into an all out riot of freethinking citrus fruit, with clockwork orange, grapefruit and mango.

fields.name: Early Start
fields.description: Industrial Irish Craft Beer IPA is dark gold in colour and is packed with fresh citrus and tropical fruit flavour with a sweet biscuit malt base and refreshing bitterness. The aroma is also full of malty character

fields.name: Zywiec 0.0%
fields.description: Pours clear, gold in color with 1/4 inch head. Taste is grass, honey, and earthy hops. Light bodied, slightly bitter, moderate carbonation.

fields.name: Steigl
fields.description: Austrian brewed Stiegl-Freibier stands out through its full-bodied, balanced taste. Aromatic Austrian Saphir hops with a particularly smooth malt-hop balance. Alcohol Free Beers are made just like the alcoholic ones with water, yeast, hops and barley.

fields.name: Stella Artois
fields.description: With a pronounced hoppy bitterness and a crisp, clean and refreshing finish, but with not even a drop of alcohol and just 60 calories, Stella Artois can now be savoured by everyone. Maybe not around the wife as a precautionary measure

fields.name: St Peter's
fields.description: A delicious alcohol free, full-bodied ale, that's dark amber in colour. It boasts a rich and malty taste that is bursting with lasting flavour, followed by a refreshing and delicate bitterness. Proudly certified by The Vegan Society.

fields.name: Budweiser
fields.description: Budweiser Zero, zero alcohol, zero sugar and only 46 calories, with the same iconic taste of budweiser. It is brewed with premium budweiser barley, hop and malt through the same expert beechwood ageing technique that delivers the smoothness of budweiser, as well as a revolutionary 4x-cold-filtration process.

fields.name: Weihenstephaner Alkoholfrei
fields.description: The pleasant spicy hops note and the full light and sweet flavour, with a slight bitterness, makes it an ideal companion for snacks, hearty salads or simply a refreshment on hot days. Brewed according to our centuries-old brewing tradition on the Weihenstephan hill.

fields.name: Sommersby Apple
fields.description: Easy drinking apple cider with a unique balanced taste. Pleasant sparkling sweetness with a fruity and sour balance for a very refreshing drink.

fields.name: Älska Strawberry & Lime
fields.description: Strawberries are the God of berries. Combined with tangy tropical lime the result is a rarely vibrant cider. Now available with 0,5% abv.500 ml 0,5% Vol

fields.name: Bulmers 0.0
fields.description: All the flavour and character you would expect from Bulmers but without the alcohol. They use a non-alcoholic fermentation to create cider character and blend with apple juice. Bulmers Alcohol Free Zero is crisp and refreshing with apple and cider notes on the aroma and aftertaste.

fields.name: Kopparberg Pear
fields.description: Refreshingly light and fruity cider. Made from fresh fruits and natural spring water

fields.name: Kopparberg Strawberry & Lime
fields.description: Combining fresh strawberry flavour with the subtle taste of lime, Kopparberg Strawberry & Lime Cider packs in maximum fruit refreshment and a revitalising taste – the perfect drink for a summer barbeque.

fields.name: Maciver
fields.description: MacIver's innovative Alcohol Free Cider is a subtle blend of our most mature ciders with the fresh juice of our fragrant dessert apples.

fields.name: Cronins 0.0%
fields.description: Cronins Cider 0.0% is the alcohol-free version of Cronins extraordinarily crisply refreshing cider made from all natural ingredients. Gluten free and vegan friendly. No Artificial Colours or Flavourings. Only 89 Calories per bottle.

fields.name: Stonewell
fields.description: With a wonderful fresh apple juice aroma and effervescence that tickles the nose this cider gives an initial burst of sweet apple flavour on the palate followed by citrus and woody notes derived from the bittersweet and Jonagored apples used as the base ciders.

fields.name: Thatchers Zero
fields.description: Thatchers Zero is a golden, medium dry, alcohol free cider with appley aromas and crisp refreshment. Crafted using a selection of our favourite cider apples, the blend of traditional and modern varieties creates an alcohol free cider with body, smoothness and character.

fields.name: Black Tower Rosé
fields.description: A rich, soft, warming rosé, full of fruit flavours but with only 232kJ/55 kcal per 125ml glass (186kJ/44kcal per 100ml) - over 30% less than standard wine with 9.5% vol. Enjoy well chilled on its own or as a great accompaniment with your favourite foods.

fields.name: Black Tower White
fields.description: A smooth, refreshing and vibrant white with rich fruit flavours but with only 232kJ/55 kcal per 125ml glass (186kJ/44kcal per 100ml) - over 30% less than standard wine with 9.5% vol. Enjoy well chilled on its own or as a great accompaniment with your favourite foods

fields.name: Eisberg Rosé
fields.description: Produced at the famous Schloss Wachenheim winery in Germany, Eisberg is the UK's best-loved non-alcoholic wine brand. Featuring notes of strawberries, raspberries and rose petals, this bright non-alcoholic Rosé wine is full-bodied and dry with a touch of acidity on the finish.

fields.name: Eisberg Merlot
fields.description: This fruity, aromatic Merlot is full bodied, lush and velvety with intense plum and blackberry flavours, with the alcohol gently removed.

fields.name: Eisberg Sauvignon Blanc
fields.description: This fresh, aromatic Sauvignon Blanc has classic gooseberry and tropical fruit flavours with the alcohol gently removed.

fields.name: Freixent
fields.description: Expect lively tropical notes and citrusy flavours. This alcohol free sparkler is a perfect alternative for a more permissible enjoyment whether is as a mid week drink or at your dinner party.

fields.name: Fre Rosé
fields.description: Faber Sparkling ROSÉ features a full-bodied, well-balanced aroma. Notes of fruity, aromatic peach lends the wine a refreshing, light character

fields.name: Fre Moscato
fields.description: FRE Alcohol-Removed Moscato has aromas of fragrant white peaches and tropical fruit, leading to round, fruity flavors and a crisp finish. Each FRE non-alcoholic wine is crafted using traditional winemaking methods.

fields.name: Las Mulas Sauvignon Blanc
fields.description: From the Curico valley in Chile , this organic beauty is named after the mules that work the vineyards and the reflection of how naturally they are maintained. It's a vision of the past in order to change the future. The wine has wonderful aromas of citrus and ripe tropical fruits are complimented by a lovely clean , crisp finish.

fields.name: Le Petit Étoilé Rosé
fields.description: Le Petit Étoilé Cabernet Rosé is an organic alcohol-free drink with a pale pink hue and bright, clear appearance. The nose offers aromas of small red fruits such as redcurrant, blackcurrant and raspberry which combine harmoniously with delicate floral and spicy notes.

fields.name: Le Petit Étoilé Chardonay
fields.description: Le Petit Étoilé Chardonnay is an organic, alcohol-free drink with a pale yellow hue and clear green glimmers. The nose disclose aromas of acacia flower and white peach combined with a touch of citrus and vanilla. The palate is fresh with a pleasant touch of acidity and a very long finish.

fields.name: McGuigan Sauvignon Blanc
fields.description: An alcohol free Sauvignon Blanc from the McGuigan Zero range. Generous aromas of gooseberry and citrus fruits, with a subtle grassy tone. This refreshing full flavoured Sauvignon Blanc delivers flavours of passionfruit and lime whilst finishing clean and crisp.

fields.name: McGuigan Rosé
fields.description: Aromatic and vibrant, the scent of garden flowers combine with fresh strawberries and citrus fruits. The palate is generous with distinct forest berry and citrus fruits leading to a clean, crisp and refreshing finish.

fields.name: McGuigan Shiraz
fields.description: Subtle spice and vanilla notes complemented by plum and forest berry aromas. This Shiraz has good length of flavour with sweet blackcurrants and a round balanced finish.

fields.name: Carl Jung Merlot
fields.description: A nice fruity alcohol free red wine typical of a table wine. It is clean on the palate and has a long finish. The nose is raspberry and red currant like a Baco Noir.

fields.name: Natureo Muscat
fields.description: A pale yellow wine which offers seductive aromas of white flowers and fresh fruit (quince, Guyot pear). The palate is warm, silky and very flavourful

fields.name: Torres Natureo Syrah
fields.description: Enjoy a lovely cherry–red wine, with aromas of pomegranate and currant, and hints of oak–imparted vanilla and toast. Round, balanced and truly clean on the palate with soft tannins and delicate acidity.

fields.name: Torres Natureo Rosé
fields.description: Alcohol-free (dealcoholized) rosé wine made from Syrah and Cabernet Sauvignon grapes. After fermentation and maceration, only the alcohol is extracted, maintaining the wine's aroma and flavor. Raspberry color, with dim bronze reflections. It has a delicate fruit aroma (cherry jam) with a vegetable notes (coffee).

fields.name: Nozeco
fields.description: Carbonated Flavored Drink Based on De-Alcoholised WineWine of France

fields.name: Le Petit Béret Muscat Doux
fields.description: A complex and vibrant ensemble: intensity of Muscat, ripe fruit aromas, harmony of fresh floral notes, fine notes of roses, lychee and ripe pineapple. Palate: Very tender, its softness brings out the aromas of pineapple, lychee and then the more delicate touch of rose petals.

fields.name: Pierre Zéro Merlot
fields.description: Intense ruby color with red fruits on the nose. This red wine shows freshness, balance and youth that delight the senses. Seductive frisky red fruit resembles the glass. In the mouth, this wine is wonderfully fresh and youthful, a sensation for the senses.

fields.name: Dr Zenzen Pino Grigio 0.0%
fields.description: Dr Zenzen Pinot Grigio is true to its Italian style in that it is a light medium sweet wine which is fresh and fruity on the palate. Fully alcohol free.

fields.name: Dr Zenzen Riesling 0.0%
fields.description: Dr Zenzen Non-Alcoholic Riesling is a non-vintage zero-alcohol white wine made in Germany. It has a clean pale lemon colour, and a clean light nose. Flavours of grapefruit, lime and peach.

fields.name: Sangre de Toro-Sauvignon Blanc 0.0
fields.description: Soft and lightly effervescent on the palate, with an exquisite citrusy finish (quince). A dealcoholized white, perfect for any occasion. Food Recommendation: An excellent aperitif; lovely with all kinds of fish, seafood and rice dishes.

fields.name: Sangre de Toro-Syran 0.0
fields.description: Pale yellow colour. Delicate floral and fruit aromas. Soft and lightly effervescent on the palate, with an exquisite citrusy finish (quince).

fields.name: Jacob's Creek Unvined
fields.description: A complex mix of plum, blackberry and chocolate spice. The lovely rounded palate offers flavours of dark berries and blackberry jam complemented by soft tannins.

fields.name: Antidote 0%
fields.description: An elegant, fine and complex nose, dominated by floral notes at first, followed by juniper and a refreshing citrus touch. Ending up with a blend of spices aromas.

fields.name: Saoirse Gin
fields.description: Saoirse Non-Alcoholic Rum Alternative €9.99/75cl – Sweet and Vibrant with notes of soft vanilla and chocolate and a hint of tropical pineapple. It's perfect to drink with Cola or Ginger Beer, or why not keep warm this winter with some hot buttered Rum Alternative.

fields.name: Saoirse Rum
fields.description: Saoirse Non-Alcoholic Rum Alternative €9.99/75cl – Sweet and Vibrant with notes of soft vanilla and chocolate and a hint of tropical pineapple. It's perfect to drink with Cola or Ginger Beer, or why not keep warm this winter with some hot buttered Rum Alternative

fields.name: Cedars Pink Rose
fields.description: Ceder's Pink Rose is soft and sweet with notes of Juniper, Rose, and Hibiscus. Rose and sweet hibiscus complement Juniper for a soft elevation of classic gin flavors.

fields.name: Clean G
fields.description: Clean G is our take on London Dry Gin. Crisp juniper, balanced with botanicals - delicious. Aromatic botanical ingredients, including real juniper are carefully sourced, blended to our secret recipe and distilled. The resulting distillate is mixed with other ingredients to create the finished non-alcoholic spirit

fields.name: Clean R
fields.description: Clean R is our take on Spiced Caribbean Rum. Warming spice, golden caramel and cayenne pepper - delicious. Big flavoured Jamaican rum is mixed with our secretly guarded blend of spices. This boldly flavoured distillate is combined with other ingredients to create the finished non-alcoholic spirit.

fields.name: Clean T
fields.description: Clean T is our take on blanco tequila; opening with soft, fresh green agave and new oak aromas and hints of olive, complemented perfectly with a medley of sweet melon and subtle fruit flavours, all culminating to a classic peppery dry finish - and a cheeky tingle on the tongue.

fields.name: Clean V
fields.description: Clean V is our expertly crafted non-alcoholic take on warming spiced apple vodka. Uplifting and crisp with a touch of cinnamon – delicious. Aromatic hints of green apple and cinnamon spice set the scene for a perfectly balanced blend of fresh and lively flavours, with a classic warm alcohol-like sensation to finish.

fields.name: Dry London
fields.description: Rich scents of orange blossom, lime, jasmine, juniper and mint. Palate: Juniper, citrus and pepperberry deliver a generous, dry finish. Rich scents of orange blossom, lime, jasmine, juniper and mint.

fields.name: Seedlip Spice 94
fields.description: Seedlip Spice 94 is a sophisticated blend of Allspice berries & Cardamom w/ warm notes from two bark distillates & a bright, zesty finish. To make our signature Seedlip & Tonic, pour 50ml over ice, top w/ tonic & garnish w/ a twist of Grapefruit peel.

fields.name: Seedlip Garden 108
fields.description: Garden 108 - A floral blend of peas & hay, with traditional herb distillates in celebration of the English countryside. Seedlip Garden 108 captures the essence of the English countryside with sophisticated top notes of Peas & Hay with a complex herbal base character of Spearmint, Rosemary & Thyme.

fields.name: GinISH
fields.description: Our alcohol-free GinISH honors the classic taste of gin, boasting the familiar notes of juniper berries and citrus. We use natural botanicals and coriander seeds to achieve that classic gin flavor and a unique distillate using the shells from chili seeds to provide that satisfying heat we love.

fields.name: Gordons 0.0
fields.description: New Gordon's Alcohol Free 0.0%. Made using only the finest distilled botanicals, just like the original Gordon's London Dry Gin, Gordon's 0.0% provides the bold, juniper led character you'd expect from Gordon's. The perfect alcohol-free alternative to your usual choice of Gordon's & tonic

fields.name: Juniper
fields.description: The ‘Juniper Edition' is made in small batches with classic gin botanicals including Juniper (the essence of Gin), angelica root, lemon, orange and grapefruit.As the name suggests the 'Juniper Edition' is juniper forward with complex aromas of lemon, orange and grapefruit.

fields.name: Kentucky 74
fields.description: Vanilla. Smokey caramel. All the traditional flavors of Kentucky bourbon make an appearance in Kentucky 74, along with an interesting heat that is reminiscent of a peppery ginger. The experience is quite flavorful and unlike anything we've seen so far in the non-alcoholic spirits category

fields.name: American Malt
fields.description: Generous flavours of vanilla and toasted nuts with herbal notes providing a complexity, offset by a long,mellow finish. Honey notes, with scents of sweet spice and charred, cedary oak. Generous flavours of vanilla and toasted nuts with herbal notes providing a complexity, offset by a long,mellow finish.

fields.name: Monday
fields.description: The nose is bold and juniper forward in classic London Dry fashion. On the palate, strong juniper throughout is accompanied by notes of bitter lemon, grapefruit with a hint of coriander. Finishes long with complexity and heat that develops over time.

fields.name: Nightcap
fields.description: This indulgent elixir is made with tree saps, aromatic plants and ancient remedies used to relax and unwind. Enjoy complex notes of wood and bright spice with a calm, dreamy feeling.

fields.name: Ritual Zero Proof
fields.description: Our non-alcoholic whiskey alternative is specially crafted to replace traditional whiskey 1:1 in the drinks you already know and love. Ritual spirits are made for cocktails and not meant to be consumed straight or neat. Overtones of vanilla and oak, with notes of stone fruit and caramel, finishing with a pleasant heat.

fields.name: RumISH
fields.description: RumISH is an award-winning, alcohol-free Rum made from natural botanicals such as Madagascar vanilla, nutmeg, baked apple and chili which provides the heat we know from typical spirits. Perfect for mixing: RumISH is not intended for pure consumption.

fields.name: Silk Tree
fields.description: Silk tree is100% natural using only fresh botanicals slowly distilled in small batches with neutral grain spirit and Irish spring water. Silk Tree contains no preservatives, sugars, colourings or artificial flavours. Silk Tree is winning rave reviews from their rapidly growing fan base.

fields.name: Social-Elixir
fields.description: This dark herbal elixir is the ultimate social companion and mood elevator. Natural, blissful feeling with lion’s mane mushroom, yerba mate and damiana. Full-bodied and bittersweet with a curious savoury bite.

fields.name: Tanqueray 0.0
fields.description: Tanqueray 0.0% allows you to discover the definitive experience from Tanqueray, just without the alcohol. Serve with your chosen tonic and garnish over ice, then sip, savour and appreciate! Tanqueray 0.0% Alcohol Free has a citrus style and juniper led profile, with a delicate botanical complexity behind it.

fields.name: Triple Sexy
fields.description: Sexy AF Triple Sexy is an alcohol free triple sec made for mocktails. Tasting like the classic triple sec, Triple Sexy is filled with botanicals like Sweet & Bitter Orange, Rosehips and many more. Our Triple Sexy has many benefits for people wishing to drink alcohol free or non alcoholic mocktails.

fields.name: Versin
fields.description: VERSIN is a non-alcoholic alternative to vermouth created with a mixture of cloves, cinnamon, ginger, citrus, to name a few. The drink is naturally sweet, caused by the combination of ingredients with natural sugars that are normally processed during fermentation.

fields.name: Whissin
fields.description: WHISSIN is a non-alcoholic alternative to whisky created with a mixture of barley, maize, and wheat. Its sweetness is caused by the combination of ingredients with natural sugars that are normally processed during fermentation.

fields.name: Zero Point Zero
fields.description: Non Alcoholic Sparkling White Wine 75cl Zero Point Zero ... Ingredients, Carbonated Water, Non-alcoholic Fermented Grape Juice Concetrate (10%)

fields.name: White Cane
fields.description: This premium non-alcoholic alternative to white rum has generous flavors with oak and sugar cane providing the perfect platform for the marzipan, orange and coconut flavors to shine through with a little peppery finish dries the palate without overwhelming it.
